<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚就是翘首以盼的万圣节活动了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在正式开始之前还有一点时间，<delay20 />
不过我已经激动起来了啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天终于等来<delay8 />万圣节了。<delay frames="40" />
我已经做好了万全的准备。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就等着开始信号啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">终于到来了，万圣节！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可要动真格啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要认真对待我的攻势啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">万圣节活动马上就要开始了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也就位吧，<delay8 />
等下不要落后于人哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节活动开始的时间就在眼前了，<delay20 />
差不多该最后检查一次准备是否充足了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再谨慎也不过分！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有一会儿就是5点了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到万圣节活动马上就要开始，<delay20 />
心里就七上八下的，静不下来啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能是因为这个月有万圣节吧，<delay20 />
可以看到<tag a="110" b="32" />上<delay8 />
零星点缀着南瓜装饰。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样<delay8 />感受着<tag a="110" b="32" />上的氛围<delay20 />
静悄悄地变为万圣节气氛，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还挺不赖的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次看到<tag a="110" b="32" />上的<delay8 />南瓜装饰，<delay20 />
我都有些心神不宁的感觉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道<delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是按捺不住心中的喜悦了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然只是一些南瓜装饰，<delay20 />
不过这个数量，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一下子提升了它们的存在感。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有这么多装饰摆着，<delay8 />万圣节当天
一定热闹非凡。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉现在<delay8 />
不管把目光投向哪里，<delay20 />
都会有数不尽的南瓜装饰映入眼帘。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节当天也会因此
气氛格外热烈吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以想见，收拾起来会相当辛苦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>